<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4>Hi, <%= @driver.name %>!</h4>
    <p>A new trip request matching your routes has been added to your list of trip requests. Proceed to your dashboard to accept, decline or view more details of the request. Below is a summary of the request.</p>
    <br/>
    <p><b>Pickup Address:</b> <%= @trip.pickup_address %> </p>
    <p><b>Destination Address:</b> <%=  @trip.destination_address %></p>
    <p><b>Pickup Date:</b> <%= @trip.pickup_date %> </p>
    <p><b>Pickup Time:</b>  <%= @trip.pickup_time %></p>
    <p><b>Estimated Price:</b> <%= @trip.driver_fee %>  </p>
    <p><a href="https://wehaul.netlify.com" target="_blank">Log In</a> to continue</p>
    <br/>
    <p>Best</p>
    <p>WeHaul Team</p>
  </body>
</html>